name: Tegucigalpa Bag
description: Tegucigalpa is located in the southern-central highland region of Honduras, the department of Francisco Morazán of which it is also the departmental capital. It is situated in a valley, surrounded by mountains and both Tegucigalpa and Comayagüela, being sister cities, are physically separated by the Choluteca River. Tegucigalpa is famous for it`s beautiful landmarks, amazing scenery, and modern architecture. Take a trip to Tegucigalpa with this bag.

name: Los Angeles Bag
description: Los Angeles is called the city of angels for a reason. This fun, festive bag is just what you need to get a taste of the L.A lifestyle, wherever you are. Whether you're celebrity-spotting in the hills, or catching up on your tan at the beach, this bag will be the perfect item to carry around.

name: Cape Town Bag
description: The city of Cape Town is famous for its beautiful architecture, warm climate, and amazing beaches. This bag design was inspired by the beautiful city, and we hope you feel a little taste of Cape Town when you wear it.

name: Miami Bag
description: Were going to Miami, welcome to Miami! Miami is famous for it's beaches, and carefree culture. We hope this bag makes you feel like you're at the beach, chilling on the boardwalk, without a care in the world. We hope this bag will give you a taste of the Miami lifestyle.

name: Stockholm Bag
description: Stockholm is the capital of Sweden. and it's famous for it's rich culture and beautiful scenery. From museums, to art galleries, to restaurants, Stockholm has it all. This bag was designed to give you a taste of that rich culture. This is the bag that you can lug around to class, or take along with you to an event.
